{"tid":2039010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港陷落了！劍橋學者：國際對中國制裁若不夠重 恐進攻台灣","createTime":"2020-05-27T22:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T12:27:05.000Z","uid":141151,"like":79,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"87553892d815978b9add1edea6e27398b2f6d1c4","tid":2039010,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T22:04:07.000Z","msg":"香港陷落了！劍橋學者：國際對中國制裁若不夠重 恐進攻台灣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3179490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3179490&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=af4c3342\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3179490&h=f7f8265c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3179490</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國近日強推「港版國安法」，讓不少港人對未來憂心忡忡。英國劍橋大學地區與國際問題研究所副研究員亞歷山大（Alexander G&ouml;rlach）遺憾地指出，香港已形同淪陷，現在國際制裁必須讓中國付出代價，否則中國下一步就是進攻、併吞台灣。<br />\n<br />\n《德國之聲》27日刊出亞歷山大的投書 ，文中提到，香港去年開始的反送中行動，讓香港特首林鄭月娥收回了送中條例修改，並在去年11月的區議會選舉中，讓香港泛民主派獲得壓倒性的勝利，似乎宣告民眾抗爭勝利；但北京卻對此惱羞成怒，所以繞開立法會提出「國安法」，藉此逮捕民主陣營人士。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">亞歷山大文中遺憾提到，香港已經淪陷，現在必須要讓中國感到「後果很嚴重」，否則，中國會自認成功而無法自拔地陷入瘋狂，下一步就是進攻台灣。</span></span></strong>亞歷山大說，台灣是一個獨立國家，然而中共處心積慮想毀掉這個離他們只有「一水相隔」的民主典範國家，北京就是害怕，台灣的民主星星之火，會燃燒到整片中國土地。<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於此，國際必須制裁中國，迫使中國遵守承諾，在這一點上，德國應該和美國、英國聯手；此外，國際更應強化與台灣的外交關係，提出台灣在受到武力攻擊時，提供軍事幫助的承諾。"},{"pid":"2b772d22871ef0e24f1888847d9096ff19f8f344","tid":2039010,"uid":35432,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T22:07:01.000Z","msg":"中国人係唔會縮嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定要打台灣統一祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b7c96624a51f16950503d6bbe08852b9013655","tid":2039010,"uid":254594,"like":10,"dislike":5,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T22:14:49.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">台灣的民主星星之火，會燃燒到整片中國土地。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難d囉<br />\n生番未開發 邊個會係支那推動民主"},{"pid":"2c438b563f2f63920955890623a8b202aaae1a05","tid":2039010,"uid":159986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T22:15:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f919b16fe38c41a6bc110bb1dae2f97e23a5a7bb","tid":2039010,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T22:15:50.000Z","msg":"心水清<br />\n有無精華版twitter戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4501906045e0e3b3ee92c31b370043ebe6ad9a66","tid":2039010,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T22:22:12.000Z","msg":"又話咩48小時攻佔全台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4795fa48c55f4684485e11199d046d040d9839","tid":2039010,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T22:25:59.000Z","msg":"這個真，過唔到聖誕唔奇"},{"pid":"83e5ef0d35cb31d382cafadaa7e2ed0a87df2d5c","tid":2039010,"uid":227271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:05:54.000Z","msg":"解放軍從不打沒準備的仗⋯"},{"pid":"825bb67e9bec3939c19d9ed9aaa7e8e3352273af","tid":2039010,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28b74f6995b6577a3f20eb23d2a1f4064ed619e","tid":2039010,"uid":321837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:09:37.000Z","msg":"台灣民主之火點會燒到中共? 周圍都係民主國家，咁未會個個都打?<br />\n無錯，的確係會個個都打"},{"pid":"082c47e9f41a6a69427c609075fb44315b10c55e","tid":2039010,"uid":6